[hr]

[size=14pt][b]Bug Reports[/b][/size]

When reporting bugs, please include:

[list]
[li]The name of the fork/mod[/li]
[li]Your Starsector version[/li]
[li]Your mod list[/li]
[li]The crash log, if applicable[/li]
[li]What you were doing when the issue occurred[/li]
[/list]

Reports like “it crashed” are hard to fix. Logs and reproduction steps help a lot.

[hr]

[size=14pt][b]Compatibility Notes[/b][/size]

These forks may touch code, data files, faction behavior, markets, variants, or translations. Compatibility will vary depending on the original mod and how much work was required.

I will try to document known conflicts when they are discovered.

[hr]

[size=14pt][b]Credits[/b][/size]

Full credit goes to the original mod authors, artists, translators, and contributors whose work made these factions possible in the first place.

This project exists because old mods are worth preserving, and good ideas should not disappear just because a version number changed.

